# Kesiyos Messaging Agent

Automated customer service agent for **Kesiyos Restaurant** (Plaza Pinares Express, Guatemala). Handles Facebook Messenger and Instagram DM conversations with AI-powered responses, three-tier message classification, and staff escalation via WhatsApp.

---

## Overview

Kesiyos receives customer messages on Facebook Messenger and Instagram asking about the menu, hours, prices, delivery, and placing orders. This agent:

- **Auto-replies** to common questions (menu, hours, location, delivery, payments) using a curated knowledge base
- **Collects order/reservation details** from customers before escalating to staff
- **Immediately escalates** complaints, large orders, allergy questions, and anything it can't handle confidently
- **Alerts staff via WhatsApp** when human attention is needed
- **Queues structured data** for future synchronization with Odoo 17 (POS + loyalty program)

### How It Works

```
Customer (FB Messenger / Instagram DM)
        ↓
   Meta Webhook POST → Nginx → FastAPI (port 8444)
        ↓
   Signature verification + deduplication
        ↓
   Claude Haiku classifies intent → generates response
        ↓
   ┌──────────────┬──────────────┬──────────────┐
   │   Tier 1     │   Tier 2     │   Tier 3     │
   │  Auto-reply  │ Gather info  │  Escalate    │
   │  (menu, hrs) │ then escalate│  immediately │
   └──────┬───────┴──────┬───────┴──────┬───────┘
          │              │              │
     Reply to       Reply to       Reply to
     customer       customer       customer
                         │              │
                    WhatsApp alert  WhatsApp alert
                    to staff        to staff
                         │              │
                    Write to        Write to
                    odoo_sync_queue odoo_sync_queue
```

---

## Three-Tier Classification

| Tier | Action | Examples |
|------|--------|---------|
| **Tier 1** | Auto-reply, no human needed | Menu prices, hours, location, delivery options, payment methods, kids menu, salsas, sides, social impact info |
| **Tier 2** | Collect details, then escalate | Orders (items, qty, dine-in/takeout/delivery, address, name), reservations (name, date, time, party size), loyalty program specifics |
| **Tier 3** | Escalate immediately | Complaints, large orders/catering, allergy questions, employment/supplier inquiries, billing requests, problems with existing orders, low confidence |

---

## Tech Stack

| Component | Technology |
|-----------|-----------|
| Backend | FastAPI (Python 3.10+) |
| AI Engine | Claude Haiku 4.5 (`claude-haiku-4-5-20251001`) |
| Database | PostgreSQL — separate `kesiyos_bot` database |
| Messaging | Meta Graph API v21.0 (Messenger + Instagram) |
| Staff Alerts | WhatsApp Cloud API |
| Reverse Proxy | Nginx |
| Process Manager | systemd |
| Future Odoo Sync | XML-RPC to Odoo 17 Community Edition |

