## Knowledge Base

The agent's knowledge base (`app/knowledge_base.md`) contains the complete Kesiyos menu with prices, combo structures, customization options, business hours, location, delivery options, payment methods, and communication tone guidelines. All responses are generated in Spanish using formal "usted" tone.

### Menu Highlights

- **Kesiyos** — Queso Q29, Pollo Q39, Carne Q39 + combo system (Solo Tú, Trío, Familiar)
- **Kesiyos Dorado** — Individual Q35 + combo system
- **Kesi-Bites** — Mini Q21, Para Compartir Q48, Familiar Q70
- **Menú Kids** — Kesiyito Q32, Doradita Q34
- **Sides, drinks, and desserts** — Full pricing in knowledge base

### Business Info

- **Location:** Plaza Pinares Express, 59 Avenida, Pinares del Norte
- **Hours:** Tuesday–Sunday, 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM (closed Monday)
- **Delivery:** Own delivery via InDrive, Uber Eats, PedidosYa
- **Payment:** Cash, card, Neo Link Pay, BI bank transfer

